{"tid":1538950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大清算開始，洗底都無用","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:30:20.000Z","uid":246671,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e597cbd71661187ab68e2cfb65ce886284aa66","tid":1538950,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"We never forget, we never forgive"},{"pid":"1c13e998a080d08750dd96e6143978a745812295","tid":1538950,"uid":246671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"e043cf7a5b49680f7ab5d82a841b5ae5d86d8c4b","tid":1538950,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"生活係我地呢一代人既唾棄之下啦，仆街"},{"pid":"85a3dc18405903a5832c8ceecdc8930261e534b4","tid":1538950,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"a0d6d1ed62fad5173c748179a3211eca236a74b5","tid":1538950,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"49393a11fb85aa7b01e052cc86408a1585c68d39","tid":1538950,"uid":20444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n仲有清算狗狗 解散狗隊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"79a63ecf7aabc06f626bd53cdb9bc26e713b422a","tid":1538950,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dec27379a1705e2978813183a0f8228785ff0985","tid":1538950,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:29:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月7 機場<br />\n9月8 美領</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"a7b15ae589ff681ec64f80403097e7be8aeae9c7","tid":1538950,"uid":246671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a63ecf7aabc06f626bd53cdb9bc26e713b422a","tid":1538950,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"必到"}]}